{"tid":1766032,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"北角29歲男子吊頸亡 警短時間內確認死者因病自殺 \b並無可疑","createTime":"2019-12-02T09:42:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T11:53:48.000Z","uid":8526,"like":3,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"26cb919e30caae9e0247b3c3894664ac95b35a74","tid":1766032,"uid":8526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:42:10.000Z","msg":"再有離奇死亡個案，一名29歲男子在北角一單位上吊死亡，沒有遺書，但警方短時間內就指是因健康問題而自殺，而香港01及東方日報等都跟著如此報導。令網民懷疑，事件是否另有內情。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191202/photo/bkn-20191202001742697-1202_00822_001_01p.jpg?20191202003152\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191202%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191202001742697-1202_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20191202003152&h=14315623&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n//昨日(1日)晚上9時許，姓方(29歲)男子在北角丹拿道8號屋苑一單位睡房以繩上吊昏迷，家人通知保安員報案，救護員趕至證實事主已死亡。警方在單位內調查，未有檢獲遺書，初步相信方因健康問題自尋短見，事件無可疑，死因有待驗屍確定。//<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"http://jellyhknews.com/r/NNnDn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjellyhknews.com%2Fr%2FNNnDn&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRQ%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=75101963\" target=\"_blank\">http://jellyhknews.com/r/NNnDn</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191202/bkn-20191202001742697-1202_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191202%2Fbkn-20191202001742697-1202_00822_001.html&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRQ%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=117f2458\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191202/bkn-20191202001742697-1202_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e23f4ead09bab567b9bb135fe061d0504992534b","tid":1766032,"uid":8526,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:43:20.000Z","msg":"點解無遺書都可以即刻知係因病自殺"},{"pid":"f7fcebd43acab5dda38eb852bd025b511c41dadd","tid":1766032,"uid":8526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:45:18.000Z","msg":"推"},